snippet.title: Mekorama Trailer
snippet.description:
Mekorama will launch Sunday, May 15, 2016 on Apple's App Store and Google's Play Store!

Find out more: http://www.mekorama.com/press/

Help a tiny robot stumble home through 50 puzzling mechanical dioramas.

- Relaxing gameplay
- Charming robots
- Collectible level cards
- Diorama maker
- Small install size

Try Mekorama for free for as long as you like. Then pay what you think it's worth. I hope you'll love it :)

Kindly,
Martin Magni
